y Maker-Michael Santos']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/opera-plus.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/operaplus.jpg" alt="Opera Plus / Tape" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/opera-plus.php">Opera Plus<br />Tape</a></h4><p>先ほどの作品と違って暖かみのある作品。共通しているのは「音楽」として意識を奪われず、自然に馴染むことですね。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0015XF8SU?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0015XF8SU" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Opera Plus-Tape']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fnoises-from-a-hill%252Fid310547314%253Fi%253D310547331%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTI" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Opera Plus-Tape']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/reich-four-organs---phase-patterns.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/fourorgans.jpg" alt="Reich: Four Organs - Phase Patterns / Steve Reich" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/reich-four-organs---phase-patterns.php">Reich: Four Organs - Phase Patterns<br />Steve Reich</a></h4><p>とてもシンプルな音ですが、音が重なることによりどんどん複雑になっていきます。BGMとして聴いても邪魔になりません。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0026UZFI4?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0026UZFI4" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Reich: Four Organs - Phase Patterns-Steve Reich']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Ffour-organs%252Fid281572342%253Fi%253D281572345%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTNAME:" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Reich: Four Organs - Phase Patterns-Steve Reich']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/surfaces-of-a-broken-marching-band.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/surface.jpg" alt="Surfaces of a Broken Marching Band / Ezekiel Honig" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/surfaces-of-a-broken-marching-band.php">Surfaces of a Broken Marching Band<br />Ezekiel Honig</a></h4><p>シンプルなアンビエントですが、ピアノの音やかすかなビートが眠気をさませてくれます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001GZB03Y?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B001GZB03Y" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Surfaces of a Broken Marching Band-Ezekiel Honig']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fepilogue%252Fid290263630%253Fi%253D290263659%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTNAME: Ez" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Surfaces of a Broken Marching Band-Ezekiel Honig']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/and-their-refinement-of-the-decline.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/andthier.jpg" alt="And Their Refinement of the Decline / Stars of the Lid" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/and-their-refinement-of-the-decline.php">And Their Refinement of the Decline<br />Stars of the Lid</a></h4><p>ストリングスが美しい作品です。ハーモニーとも言えない不思議な音程ですがBGMとしても活用できます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000NIIUX8?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000NIIUX8" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'And Their Refinement of the Decline-Stars of the Lid']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Feven-if-youre-never-awake%252Fid218111332%253Fi%253D218111674%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'And Their Refinement of the Decline-Stars of the Lid']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/northern.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/northern.jpg" alt="Northern / Taylor Deupree" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/northern.php">Northern<br />Taylor Deupree</a></h4><p>BGMとしてかけると鳴っているのか鳴っていないのかわからなくなるほど環境にとけ込んできます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0011F0882?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0011F0882" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Northern-Taylor Deupree']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fnovember%252Fid213703120%253Fi%253D213707495%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTNAME: Ta" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Northern-Taylor Deupree']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/ceiling-songs.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/ceiling.jpg" alt="Ceiling Songs / Ethan Rose" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/ceiling-songs.php">Ceiling Songs<br />Ethan Rose</a></h4><p>筆者のお気に入りの作品。オフィスでもBGMとして利用しています。静かですが心が落ち着く温かい音です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000H8RV7A?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000H8RV7A" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Ceiling Songs-Ethan Rose']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fsong-one%252Fid269745405%253Fi%253D269745416%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTNAME: Et" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Ceiling Songs-Ethan Rose']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/digital-headrest.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/digitalheadrest.jpg" alt="Digital Headrest / Accelera Deck" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/digital-headrest.php">Digital Headrest<br />Accelera Deck</a></h4><p>ビートがありますが、ポップさがあって柔らかいイメージのある音楽なので作業に集中ができます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00005NBOQ?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00005NBOQ" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Digital Headrest-Accelera Deck']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fferment%252Fid298005936%253Fi%253D298005969%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTN